@GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7070
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Search all (users + posts)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search?q=john&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Search users only
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search?q=john&type=users&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Search posts only
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search?q=hello&type=posts&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Search with filters (date range + location + sort by recent)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search?q=travel&type=posts&dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-12-31&sortBy=recent&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Autocomplete suggestions (all types)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/suggest?q=dan
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Autocomplete suggestions (users only)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/suggest?q=dan&type=users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Autocomplete suggestions (posts only)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/suggest?q=hel&type=posts
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Trending posts (last week, top 10)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/trending?timeWindow=week&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Trending posts (last 24 hours)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/trending?timeWindow=day&size=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Trending posts (last month, top 20)
GET {{GoingMy.Search.API_HostAddress}}/api/search/trending?timeWindow=month&size=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
